{"tid":2243721,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"年初遭警公園襲擊　涉藏毒露宿者囚室自殺","createTime":"2020-10-15T03:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T05:33:31.000Z","uid":6497,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"9f91aa0152955b9947b31ac8ce4a942f8faca720","tid":2243721,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:03:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201015/s00002/1602698796194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201015%2Fs00002%2F1602698796194&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=1b6b8ab0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201015%2Fs00002%2F1602698796194&h=b7357d9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201015/s00002/1602698796194</a><br />\n【明報專訊】一名於小欖精神病治療中心還押候訊的54歲、涉嫌藏毒的越南裔男子，原定昨日在西九龍裁判法院提堂，他上周四於囚室內以長褲纏頸自殺，送院搶救後翌日不治。懲教署稱已把事件通知警方，死因裁判法庭將召開死因研訊。<br />\n<br />\n曾協助死者的牧師林國璋證實，死者為露宿者Le Van Muoi黎民十（圖），人稱阿十，其生前同鄉好友利越春同樣涉及管有危險藥物等罪被捕，同於昨日提堂。林稱，二人亦為本年初通州街公園警員襲擊露宿者案的受害者兼目擊者，認為二人被捕不尋常。他說對阿十死訊感突然，稱他曾多次進出監獄，難以想像他會自殺。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，二人分別於9月底及上周六被捕。阿十一案終止聆訊，阿春一案則押後至下月24日。<br />\n<br />\n有通州街公園露宿者投訴今年2月被警員「屈」藏械及藏毒，被襲擊及砸爛家當，警方事後拘捕9名深水埗警區特別職務隊警員。"},{"pid":"34e184857a38ec74f1ed1097b9044ef025f0722d","tid":2243721,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:05:14.000Z","msg":"被？"},{"pid":"ba4ca88824b17ce674b28208fdb1f21f5c6b412e","tid":2243721,"uid":4574,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:07:17.000Z","msg":"被自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3662e14028268b743261c0d8d4cae9d930d5c475","tid":2243721,"uid":255637,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘩 獄中自殺埋 仲要關班狗事既單案"},{"pid":"a19c2b6715b5b02e8aa3763ed81ba1836a133796","tid":2243721,"uid":22556,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:09:38.000Z","msg":"無左證人 果9個警察無罪釋放"},{"pid":"201c411e51743ecfdaa429c0998e9baaeef8c1cf","tid":2243721,"uid":274161,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:10:44.000Z","msg":"果然中港融合，香港開始追上中國腳步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6bf7cfc6eb569d2e300ec4a11570d9115cb6d96","tid":2243721,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6159ec8de8561693469794968d92466eb402a693","tid":2243721,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d50f3ac8a590bc092fea9afbe3c6dd0f810e701","tid":2243721,"uid":160102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:11:26.000Z","msg":"又會咁啱？"},{"pid":"e4e310060958d0349f1c65eb3d628bf1ce626f49","tid":2243721,"uid":180814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:13:39.000Z","msg":"又幾巧合<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d9c4549b27a04ab14663487fc2b4a2d32895e8","tid":2243721,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7215a62231660ff27bf9252a6ac8bd61fe2f14","tid":2243721,"uid":115174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:15:06.000Z","msg":"無法無天<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371cc26fa33e8e6e4c09dfc7d270b5de6161db85","tid":2243721,"uid":185121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20